                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_provincialPriorityResultsRepeater_ctl00_ResultItem1';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Volkswagen/Jetta/Mississauga/Ontario/5_30214976_20100903134221117/?ursrc=ppl&showcpo=ShowCPO';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl03_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = true;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Volkswagen/Jetta/Brantford/Ontario/5_31033615_ON20070704162744807/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=4_100_501';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl17_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Volkswagen/Jetta/Newmarket/Ontario/5_31013064_ON20070704174645978/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=18_100_501';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl21_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Volkswagen/Jetta/Kitchener/Ontario/5_31008387_ON20080521103949086/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=22_100_501';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl22_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Volkswagen/Jetta/Kitchener/Ontario/5_31008369_ON20080521103949086/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=23_100_501';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl23_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Volkswagen/Jetta/Cambridge/Ontario/5_31007661_ON20070704162650853/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=24_100_501';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl24_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Volkswagen/Jetta/Brampton/Ontario/5_31006834_20100325063037368/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=25_100_501';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl29_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Volkswagen/Jetta/Milton/Ontario/5_30990366_ON20080206114744304/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=30_100_501';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl34_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = true;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Volkswagen/Jetta/Vaughan/Ontario/5_30980059_ON20090624113713082/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=35_100_501';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl36_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Volkswagen/Jetta/Hamilton/Ontario/5_30979241_ON20080116102945140/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=37_100_501';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl44_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Volkswagen/Jetta/Toronto/Ontario/5_30971157_ON20070704162453744/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=45_100_501';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl45_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Volkswagen/Jetta/Brampton/Ontario/5_30970802_ON20070704163013963/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=46_100_501';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl50_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = true;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Volkswagen/Jetta/Fonthill/Ontario/5_30966113_ON20070704162803088/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=51_100_501';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl51_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = true;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Volkswagen/Jetta/Fonthill/Ontario/5_30966112_ON20070704162803088/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=52_100_501';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>
            
    
	</div>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl57_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Volkswagen/Jetta/Toronto/Ontario/5_30947826_ON20071113151351022/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=58_100_501';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl62_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Volkswagen/Jetta/Maple/Ontario/5_30944583_20121029112932273/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=63_100_501';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl64_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = true;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Volkswagen/Jetta/St+Catharines/Ontario/5_30940958_ON20071122102246014/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=65_100_501';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl65_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = true;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Volkswagen/Jetta/St+Catharines/Ontario/5_30940434_ON20071122102246014/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=66_100_501';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl66_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Volkswagen/Jetta/St+Catharines/Ontario/5_30940057_ON20071122102246014/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=67_100_501';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl68_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Volkswagen/Jetta/Kitchener/Ontario/5_30938770_ON20080331102352937/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=69_100_501';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl69_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Volkswagen/Jetta/Cambridge/Ontario/5_30938496_ON20070704162650853/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=70_100_501';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl79_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = true;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Volkswagen/Jetta/Fonthill/Ontario/5_30899295_ON20070704162803088/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=80_100_501';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl82_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Volkswagen/Jetta/Cambridge/Ontario/5_30896290_ON20070704162650853/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=83_100_501';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl96_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Volkswagen/Jetta/Innisfil/Ontario/5_30889361_ON20070723114304291/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=97_100_501';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl97_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Volkswagen/Jetta/Newmarket/Ontario/5_30889040_ON20070704174645978/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=98_100_501';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

	googletag.cmd = googletag.cmd || [];

		var gads = document.createElement('script');
		gads.async = true; gads.type = 'text/javascript';
		var useSSL = 'https:' == document.location.protocol;
		gads.src = (useSSL ? 'https:' : 'http:') + '//www.googletagservices.com/tag/js/gpt.js';

		node.parentNode.insertBefore(gads, node);

		var billboardBanner = $('body', $('#Billboard_Banner iframe').contents());
		if (billboardBanner && billboardBanner.text() != '' && !billboardBanner.data('tracked')) {
			wa_trackEvent('LocalEdge', 'Banner Served', 'Search Takeover');
			billboardBanner.data('tracked', true)
		}
		var masthead = $('.at_masthead.localEdge3');
		if (masthead && masthead.css('background-image') && masthead.css('background-image') != 'none' && !masthead.data('tracked')) {
			wa_trackEvent('LocalEdge', 'Banner Served', 'V3');
			masthead.data('tracked', true)
		}
		});
		googletag.enableServices();
		googletag.display('gpt-ad-leaderboard');
		googletag.display('gpt-ad-bb1');
		googletag.display('gpt-ad-midlist');
